  "industry_note": "UNS S30300 / EN 1.4305 / X8CrNiS18-9 / JIS SUS303 — sulfur-modified 304 (S 0.15-0.35) — machinability boost (rating ~80, vs 304 의 40%). σy 240 / UTS 580 / El 50%. Tmax 815°C. ⚠ S 함량으로 weldability 매우 poor (sulfide network 가 crack starter — 일반적으로 weld 가능, 단 S-free 304 filler + 낮은 heat input). Lathe-machined parts: shaft, valve stem, bushing, knob, fittings (high-volume turning). 304 의 ~10% premium.",
